Package core

Interface IUtils

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IEntity, IEntityData, IImaginary, IMaterial, ITransform, IVec
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Color, Curve, Curve2, Curve3, CurveEntity2, CurveEntity3, Entity, EntityData, Imaginary, Material, MaterialPImage, MaterialSolid, MaterialUV, Mesh, Mesh2, Mesh3, MeshEntity2, MeshEntity3, Quaternion, Random, Transform, Transform2, Transform3, Utils, Vec, Vec2, Vec3, Vec4
    public interface IUtils
    Holds mathematical constants used by the rest of the library. Provides convenience functions for printing a hash code and identity hash code as hexadecimal strings.
